m:.0001pt;\r\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\n	font-size:10.0pt;\r\n	font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n	mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n	mso-ansi-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-fareast-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-bidi-language:#0400;}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;![endif]--&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:yes&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18.0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:yes&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;精准扶贫路上的工商人&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18.0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:18.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0cm;text-indent:31.5pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.1;line-height:21.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:black&quot;&gt;中&lt;b&gt;国硒都网讯（通讯员&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15.0pt;font-family:Arial;color:black&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:black&quot;&gt;谭田）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15.0pt&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15.0pt&quot;&gt;月&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;22&lt;/span&gt;日，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:black&quot;&gt;蓝色的天幕上嵌着一轮金光灿烂的太阳，一片白云像碧海上的孤帆在晴空飘游。冬至的一场飘洒雨后，阳光带着清新的空气飞来，冬日的阳光显得格外美丽。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15.0pt;font-family:Arial;color:black&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:18.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0cm;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15.0pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:black&quot;&gt;六角亭工商所的&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15.0pt;\r\nfont-family:Arial;color:black&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15.0pt;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;color:black&quot;&gt;名干部职工带着他们全所职工的捐款及物品来到恩施市高桥坝村，为他们的扶贫贫困户在寒冷冬日送去一丝温暖。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15.0pt;font-family:Arial;color:black&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:18.0pt;margin-left:\r\n0cm;text-indent:39.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.6;line-height:21.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:black&quot;&gt;经过近一个小时的车程我们来到高桥坝贫困户李家兵的家中，李家兵正在回家路上利用自己的拐杖慢慢地行走着，李家兵&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15.0pt;font-family:Arial;color:black&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:black&quot;&gt;本人有腿疾，因病致贫。年初见到他时还卧床不起，经过一年的康复现在可以利用拐杖慢慢行走了。看着工商所这些熟悉的面孔，他的嘴角露出了一丝微笑，连忙为我们开门。所长黄冬和书记王本维将我所职工捐赠的慰问金递在李家兵手中，平日里不怎么爱说话的他，此时感动地更不知道说什么了，激动的连说两个&ldquo;谢谢&rdquo;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15.0pt;font-family:Arial;color:black&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15.0pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:black&quot;&gt;我们知道对于一个不爱说话不善于表达的人来说，这两个字蕴含了许多他想表达的东西。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:15.0pt;font-family:Arial;color:black&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://61.136.205.130:8089/userfiles/exam/1482716547714.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width:80%;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;!--[if gte mso 9]&gt;&lt;xml&gt;\r\n &lt;w:WordDocument&gt;\r\n  &lt;w:View&gt;Normal&lt;/w:View&gt;\r\n  &lt;w:Zoom&gt;0&lt;/w:Zoom&gt;\r\n  &lt;w:PunctuationKerning/&gt;\r\n  &lt;w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing&gt;7.8 磅&lt;/w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing&gt;\r\n  &lt;w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery&gt;0&lt;/w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery&gt;\r\n  &lt;w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery&gt;2&lt;/w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery&gt;\r\n  &lt;w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/&gt;\r\n  &lt;w:SaveIfXMLInvalid&gt;false&lt;/w:SaveIfXMLInvalid&gt;\r\n  &lt;w:IgnoreMixedContent&gt;false&lt;/w:IgnoreMixedContent&gt;\r\n  &lt;w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText&gt;false&lt;/w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText&gt;\r\n  &lt;w:Compatibility&gt;\r\n   &lt;w:SpaceForUL/&gt;\r\n   &lt;w:BalanceSingleByteDoubleByteWidth/&gt;\r\n   &lt;w:DoNotLeaveBackslashAlone/&gt;\r\n   &lt;w:ULTrailSpace/&gt;\r\n   &lt;w:DoNotExpandShiftReturn/&gt;\r\n   &lt;w:AdjustLineHeightInTable/&gt;\r\n   &lt;w:BreakWrappedTables/&gt;\r\n   &lt;w:SnapToGridInCell/&gt;\r\n   &lt;w:WrapTextWithPunct/&gt;\r\n   &lt;w:UseAsianBreakRules/&gt;\r\n   &lt;w:DontGrowAutofit/&gt;\r\n   &lt;w:UseFELayout/&gt;\r\n  &lt;/w:Compatibility&gt;\r\n  &lt;w:BrowserLevel&gt;MicrosoftInternetExplorer4&lt;/w:BrowserLevel&gt;\