质的一个重要方面。不学礼，无以立。文明礼仪是个人成长的根基，是社会发展的客观要求，是人类进步的重要标志。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;沐抚中学地处恩施大峡谷旅游景区，教师&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;45&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;名，学生&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;700&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;多名，生源主要来自农村，&ldquo;知书达礼，礼行笃学&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n仿宋;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;&rdquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;是我校一直坚持的办学理念。为此，结合我校师资情况以及家长意愿，我们将&ldquo;礼&rdquo;定位为我校的核心文化，明确了以&ldquo;礼文化教育&rdquo;为特色发展方向，以&ldquo;培养学生慧中秀外素养&rdquo;为目标，全面提高学校教育质量。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:yes&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;二、指导思想&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:yes&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:22.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;为了全面实施&ldquo;读书明理，做人成才&rdquo;的理念，提升师生文明礼仪水平和综合素质，营造文明、和谐、互敬的校园人文环境，学校决定将&ldquo;礼&rdquo;文化建设作为我校继承民族文化精髓、丰富管理内涵、增强管理软实力、提高学校竞争力的长期内涵发展规划，为了更好地推进这项工作，我校&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast