t;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;4468&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;德育工作措施有层次有针对性对学生实施思想道德指导和文明养成教育，以日常行为规范教育入手，使学生从&ldquo;要我这样做&rdquo;转变为&ldquo;我应该这样做&rdquo;，让良好的行为习惯内化为学生的自觉行为，逐步让学生养成良好的道德情操、行为习惯。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;二、第二阶段：开展实施阶段&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot;&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:yes&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:22.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;根据沐抚中心学校&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;4468&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;德育工作措施的部分内容，我们对学生提出要求，明确具体、详细的文明礼仪常规，使每个学生心中有数，然后重视第一次文明礼仪训练。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;礼仪贵在实践。为充分践行礼仪知识，我校开展了形式多样的礼文化实践活动：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast&quot;&gt;在全校&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;开展&ldquo;眼睛看陋习&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;----&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast&quot;&gt;我身边的不文明行为&rdquo;调查活动，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;学生&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast&quot;&gt;可&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;选择自己身边的亲人、朋友、同学为调查对象，调查结束后，对调查的结果进行收集、整理，并对调查结果进行分析，撰写调查报告。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;、在七年级以&ldquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast&quot;&gt;文明礼仪记心中&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;&rdquo;为主题开展经典诵读活动，如：《三字经》《弟子规》《道德经》《论语》《朝读经典》等，搜集经典尊老爱幼、互帮互助、明礼诚信的故事，在班级开展讲故事比赛活动。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;、在八年级以&ldquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast&quot;&gt;文明礼仪伴我行&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;&rdquo;为主题开展文明礼仪知识竞赛活动，办一期文明礼仪手抄报活动。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;、在九年级以&ldquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast&quot;&gt;文明礼仪展风采&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;&rdquo;开展文明礼仪征文及演讲活动。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;、定期组织部分学生会成员成立校园文明督导队，利用课余时间、就餐时间进行检查，及时纠正学生的不文明行为。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;利用秋假，要求学生参与秋收劳动实践、家务劳动、家庭环境卫生整治等相关活动。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;、定期在团员中开展&ldquo;保护环境，爱护家园&rdquo;的活动。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast&quot;&gt;特别是&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;803&lt;/span&gt;班同学在班主任的组织下开展了以&ldquo;发挥森林优势，共建美丽乡村&rdquo;为主题的科技实践创新活动，唤醒了学生们参与植树造林，美化家园的主人翁意识，通过&ldquo;小手拉大手&rdquo;活动，带动学生家人和身边更多的人投入到环境保护的队伍中来。使美化环境的意识深入人心。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;、在教师队伍中开展以&ldquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast&quot;&gt;崇尚师德，丹心育人&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&rdquo;为主题的师德演讲活动，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;着力解决在教师队伍中存在的不注重细节、思想守旧、缺乏职业理想和创业激情等与新时期教育形式不相协调的教育思想和行为，培养&ldquo;礼仪之师&rdquo;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;三、第三阶段：展示深化阶段&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:22.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;礼仪重在展示。为充分展示学校文明礼仪教育的成效，学校组织开展了以&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast&quot;&gt;&ldquo;弘民族文化，展青春风采&rdquo;为主题的第五届校园文化体育科技艺术节活动，在系列体育活动中，教育&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;学生要像奥运健儿一样，在成长过程中，不怕困难，不怕挫折，积极进取；在艺术节的系列活动，展示了学生积极向上、奋发进取的精神面貌；在文化节的系列活动中，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast&quot;&gt;学生们尽情享受传统民族文化的魅力，诵读经典，传承文化，进一步推动了校园文化建设；通过本次文化艺术节培养了学生集体主义精神、良好的艺术修养和健康的审美情趣。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:22.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast&quot;&gt;同时，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;孩子的健康成长，需要家庭、学校、全社会共同来精心护理，精心培育，需要家长们为孩子创设一个和善、温馨、快乐、平等、民主、和谐的家庭育人环境，需要家长们&ldquo;做榜样、抓点滴&rdquo;。为形成学生良好的文明礼仪行为习惯，促进孩子们良好的道德养成，培养他们正确的处世态度和做人原则，学校成立了家长委员会，不定期召开家长会，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast&quot;&gt;以家长会为纽带，让&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;家长看到自己孩子在校学习生活和能力表现。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\r\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;另外，通过家校的信息沟通，传达学校对家长的要求，全体教师也不定期地进行家访，切实做到在学校进行文明礼仪教育的同时，加强家长的榜样教育力量，使他们也能在一点一滴中，在举手投足间，对子女进行文明礼仪教育。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:yes&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;四、第三阶段：总结表彰阶段&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;、开展&ldquo;文明礼仪之星&rdquo;评选活动。以班级为单位，参照学校制定的评选标准，先选出符合条件的学生，再由班级同&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast&quot;&gt;学进行投票，最后根据票数的多少，每班各选出五名&ldquo;文明礼仪之星&rdquo;，期末参评&ldquo;沐抚中学十佳礼仪学生&rdquo;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;并把其照片和事迹材料张贴于学校宣传栏内。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;、对在组织活动中表现突出的班级结合到&ldquo;文明班级&rdquo;考核量化评比中。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:22.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;\r\nline-height:150%;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;古人云：&ldquo;不学礼无以立，人无礼则不生，事无礼则不成，国无礼则不宁。&rdquo;我国自古以来就是&ldquo;礼仪之邦&rdquo;，讲文明、重礼貌、和善待人是我们中华民族世代相传的传统美德。我校将围绕文明礼仪教育主题，抓好校园建设，开展师生共讲礼仪，整合德育资源，形成教育合力，实行全员育人，做到教书育人、服务育人、环境育人、文化育人、风气育人。通过校风、校训，引导学生学做真人，教育学生团结友爱、互帮互助，通过美化、净化、绿化校园，让学生置身于整洁、清新、优美又有文化氛围的环境中，受到潜移默化的熏陶，从而达到净化心灵的目的。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:22.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:22.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:22.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nline-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:right;text-indent:22.0pt;\r\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%&quot; align=&quot;right&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n11.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:yes&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:yes&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp