-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 15pt; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 15pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15pt; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;通过这些活动普及了市民防灾减灾知识，增强全社会防灾减灾意识，推广全民避灾自救技能，同时，也将极大地提高综合减灾能力，最大限度地减轻自然灾害对广大人民群众生命财产造成的损失。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 15pt; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 15pt; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h1 align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: center; line-height: 22.5pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18pt; font-family: 方正小标宋简体;&quot;&gt;恩施市民政局全面开展&ldquo;节能宣传周&rdquo;活动&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://61.136.205.130:8089/userfiles/exam/1480043754369.png&quot; style=&quot;width:80%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:31.35pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.96&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;月&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;12&lt;/span&gt;日至&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;18&lt;/span&gt;日是全国节能宣传周，&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;月&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;14&lt;/span&gt;日是全国低碳日。为了深入进行全民节能低碳的宣传教育，让创新、协调、绿色、开放、共享的发展理念深入人心，恩施市民政局在民政系统全面展开了节能宣传周的活动。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:31.35pt;mso-char-indent-count:1.96&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;一是在机关大楼里的进门处、楼道间、卫生间等醒目位置，粘贴了节能低碳的宣传画册；二是利用微信平台、&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;QQ&lt;/span&gt;群等多种公共服务平台，提出了积极参与节能低碳活动，用实际行动支持绿色发展的倡议；三是搭建了&ldquo;节能宣传台&rdquo;，将&ldquo;节能低碳&rdquo;的宣传资料提供给广大干部职工阅读；四是利用&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;LED&lt;/span&gt;显示屏滚动宣传播放&ldquo;节能领跑、绿色发展&rdquo;的宣传语，让节能低碳的环保理念深入干部职工的人心。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\