-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;&ldquo;您坐到轮椅上试试&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;&ldquo;政府好呀，自己的亲爹都不会这样对自己呀&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;月&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;19&lt;/span&gt;日，黄坤华的新家里传来这样的对话。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;原来是市民政局两位干部为精准扶贫户黄坤华老人送来了轮椅。老人在老伴和两位干部的帮助下坐上轮椅，一直笑着，一边说着感谢政府的话，一边憧憬着在院坝里晒太阳或坐着轮椅走亲访友的情景。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;老人风湿病长年卧床，多年没出过屋子，以前家处偏僻，日常的生产和生活物资进出全靠老伴长年肩挑背驼，在几处山高路徒处还只能爬行。随着精准扶贫工作的推进，今年&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;政府出资为老人买了新房，为了老人出行方便，民政局的干部又送来了轮椅。一直生活压抑、脾气古怪的老人近来也是心情舒畅。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16pt; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;'),
