kground-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;以科学发展观为指导，全面贯彻党的十八大精神，紧紧围绕社会主义核心价值体系，继续把文明单位的创建作为学校内涵发展的总抓手，提炼学校精神，培育校园文化，不断提高学校的精神文明建设水平和师生的文明素质。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;二、创建目标&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: -0.1pt; text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;以提升师生综合素质和学校文明程度为核心，紧紧围绕市教育系统文明单位测评指标体系，重点突出教育局的年度重点推进工作，凸显学校在深入学习科学发展观实践活动、爱国主义教育活动、校园歌曲大家唱活动、师德建设系列活动、廉洁教育等方面的做法和有效经验。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt; &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 24.1pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;三、创建措施&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;（一）加强思想道德建设，提高师生文明素质。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;、强化师资队伍建设，全面提高师德水平。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;师资队伍建设是学校建设的永恒主题，也是学校发展的根本动力。沙地乡中心小学要在取得一定成绩的基础上，进一步适应时代要求，向前发展，最可靠的保证仍然是建设一支较高素质的教师队伍。学校将进一步从人格魅力、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;学术魅力两个方面加强师德、师能建设，广泛发扬先进教师和群体的事迹。广大教职员工是决定学校发展的根本力量，也是新一轮精神文明创建工作的主体。因此，新一轮的创建工作一定要与师资队伍建设规划融为一体、与学校发展规划融为一体。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;（&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;）以师德建设为龙头，不断提高教师的思想道德素质。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;学校将继续把师德教育放在教师队伍建设的首要地位来抓：进一步规范学习制度，虚事实做，形成&ldquo;讲学习&rdquo;的氛围。党员学习、教职工学习等都要坚持制度，规范管理，有计划、有安排、有主题、有记录、有小结，学习要紧跟形势，内容充实，重点突出，紧扣实际，形式多样，以解决思想困惑和工作、学习难题为切入口，力争学有实效，通过学习，提高理论素养，武装头脑，指导实践，促进工作。\r\n&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;（&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;）认真学习《中小学教师职业道德规范》、《师德师风建设的若干规定》等文件，在加强师德理论学习的同时，采取多种形式，树立学校的师德先进榜样，弘扬先进，宣传先进、学习先进。不断完善学校教师职业道德规范，严格执行师德考核制度，执行师德&ldquo;三不准&rdquo;，实行&ldquo;师德一票否决制&rdquo;。并把教师育人能力也列入教师考核内容，不断提高学生对师德的满意率。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;（&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;）贯彻落实《公民道德建设实施纲要》，持续开展社会公德、职业道德、家庭美德教育，大力倡导&ldquo;爱国守法、明礼诚信、团结友善、勤俭自强、敬业奉献&rdquo;\r\n的公民道德规范，树立良好的社会形象。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;、努力提高德育工作的实效性，全面提高学生的综合素质。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;在继续贯彻《中共中央、国务院关于加强未成年人思想道德建设若干意见》、《中小学生在校一日常规》等一系列文件的基础上，全面贯彻落实市乡德育工作会议精神，不断强化德育的核心地位，以爱国主义教育为主旋律，以队伍建设为保证，以常规教育为抓手，进一步改进德育工作的方式方法，大力推进素质教育。构建学校、社会、家庭三位一体的&ldquo;全员育人，全程育人，全方位育人&rdquo;的主体德育框架，推动学校精神文明建设的进一步深化。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 18pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;（&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;）努力夯实德育常规工作&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;以社会主义核心价值体系为引领，对学生进行社会主义荣辱观教育。加强公民道德教育，开展日常行为规范养成教育和训练，有检查、有评比，成效明显。有定期的校风检查制度、有推进校风建设的措施和活动。和社区学校、校外教育基地等联合，构建学校课外活动体系。重视贫困学生帮困助学工作。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 18pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;（&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;）切实推进文明班级建设&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;通过文明班级建设，形成师生&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;求实、创新、勤奋、向上的教与学氛围。&ldquo;文明班级&rdquo;的建设主要从以下四个方面努力。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;一是把握师生、生生关系的和谐、互动，班主任、任课教师、学生之间相互尊重、真诚互助，集中展示各自的人格魅力和才华，营造师生共同成长的精神家园。二是营造良好氛围，面向所有学生和教师，以班级建设为基础，挖掘课内外文化内涵，促进师生人格和心理的健康成长。三是传承优秀文明传统，跟上时代步伐，在诸多的和谐关系中重视自身的和谐，在潜移默化中实现师生共同的价值追求。四是拓展育人载体，充分利用地域文化资源的熏陶、家长委员会的作用、学校校外辅导员的力量，覆盖课内、课外两个领域的建设，挖掘课内外文化育人内涵，促进素质教育的深入实施。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;（&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;）充分发挥团队活动作用&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;在&ldquo;素质教育&rdquo;和&ldquo;新课程改革&rdquo;的双重作用下，开展丰富多彩的少先队活动就尤为显得重要。充分发挥少先队的教育基地作用，不断丰富少先队活动是少先队工作的根本任务，通过形式多样的活动，为队员们搭建展示个人才艺与能力的平台，让队员们在活动中去体验、总结，以达到教育的目的。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;（&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;）有效落实学科德育渗透&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 26.25pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;坚持以&ldquo;两纲&rdquo;为抓手的社会主义核心价值体系教育，重点突出以爱国主义为核心的民族精神教育和以改革创新为核心的时代精神教育与实践，重点突出社会主义荣辱观教育的主题实践活动。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 15.75pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;学科德育、德育课程以及拓展型、研究型课程、专题教育，要充分体现&ldquo;两纲&rdquo;精神。要积极开展学生生命教育与心理健康教育的实践体验活动。尤其要充分发挥思想品德课的主渠道作用，加强思品教研建设，转变教师的教育观念，通过鼓励教师开展符合时代特点的教育模式、方法、手段的探索与研究，增加实践教学环节，课堂教学要紧密联系社会和学生两个实际，采用启发式、讨论式和研究性等生动活泼的方式组织教学，充分发挥学生学习主动性，增强主渠道课的针对性、生动性和高效性。各科教学都必须紧扣学科特点，渗透德育，落实&ldquo;两纲&rdquo;教育。要坚持主旋律教育，增强学生的民族自尊心、自信心和民族自豪感，做好升降国旗仪式，完善国旗下的讲话制度。进一步健全学校、家庭、社会育人网络，形成德育工作的整体合力。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 9.05pt; text-indent: 15.75pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;学校要通过师德与育德能力的校本培训，努力提升教师人文素养、班主任综合素养、教师师德与育德能力。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 9.05pt; text-indent: 15.75pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;（&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;）积极探索社会实践途径&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;学校要积极探索课程改革与社会资源利用的教育教学实践，确保学生实践的时间。要加强社会实践环节，通过社会实践强化学生社会责任感，继续完善少先队的建设，继续抓好社区活动、春秋季各年级的社会实践活动，积极引导学生参加&ldquo;希望工程&rdquo;、&ldquo;手拉手&rdquo;、&ldquo;爱心助学&rdquo;等活动。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;以&ldquo;爱国守法，明礼诚信，团结友爱，勤俭自强，敬业奉献&rdquo;的基本道德规范和学生日常行为规范为准则，加强学生行为习惯的养成教育。要进一步健全完善家长委员会、家长学校，加强家校联系和对家庭教育的指导，构建家庭、社会、学校三位一体的育人框架。积极开展德育科研，不断提升德育层次，切实提高德育的实效性。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;（二）加强党组织的建设，充分发挥核心作用。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;、大力加强组织建设&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;认真贯彻民主集中制，坚持校长负责制，建立并执行集体领导与分工负责相结合的制度。班子和谐，定期开好民主生活会。支部活动正常，形式创新，有战斗力，发挥政治核心作用明显。坚持&ldquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;三会一课&rdquo;制度。组织生活会、民主生活会和党员汇报评议制度健全，维护党员民主权利，强化监督制约机制。建立健全党员经常性教育的长效机制，抓好党员教育管理。认真搞好党员发展工作，重视发展业务骨干、优秀青年入党。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;、有效落实党风廉政建设&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;经常开展党员干部反腐倡廉教育活动。认真落实述职述廉、经济责任审计等各项制度。积极推进廉洁教育进课堂。在招生、收费、办学等各项工作中遵守法律法规。设立校长热线、支部信箱等；学校及时向来信来访当事人反馈处理结果；违规违纪等问题查处及时高效。规范行政事业性和代办服务性收费，必须实行收费公示制度，提供财政部门的收据。预算管理规范。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;、切实做好党群工作&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 15.75pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;认真落实党和政府的相关政策，有具体措施，保障统战对象和退休教职工的各项权益。发挥老干部在关心下一代工作中的作用。扎实做好少数民族工作。工青妇工作机制健全，制度完善，有经费保障。维护教职工和女教职工的合法权益，关心困难教职工。开展学习型班组建设等活动。团的建设有凝聚力、有活力、有创新，团组织活动有特色。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 15.75pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;、广泛开展文明创建工作&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;学校由党小组牵头，制定创建计划；创建有具体的措施、落实有经费的保障、成效有考核来进行评价。有创建规划，任务目标明确。开展文明科室、文明班级等基础性创建活动。文明和谐创建活动的师生知晓率和参与率&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;100%&lt;/span&gt;。&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;（三）深化学校内涵发展，提升学校办学绩效&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 21pt; line-height: 150%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: in